<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The 'since_id' parameter is casting to integer, but it should be a float in Zend_Service_Twitter in the following functions:
- statusFriendsTimeline()
- statusReplies()
- directMessageMessages()
- directMessageSent()</p>

<p>Please inspect the following line in each function:
$_params['since_id'] = (int) $value;</p>

